    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div><p><strong>Action</strong> - 1 Creature (Touch) - 5th Level (Abjuration) - VSM<br /></p><p><strong>Materials</strong>: You require 0.2 pounds of pure @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wV3r0XKYOLYdI0nz]{Diamond Dust}, typically valued at 100 gold. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><strong>Healing Spell<br /></strong><br />You imbue a creature you touch with positive energy to undo one of the following debilitating effects.</p><ul><li>Reduce the target's exhaustion level by one</li><li>One effect that charmed or petrified the target</li><li>One curse, including the target's attunement to a cursed magic item</li><li>Any reduction to one of the target's ability scores</li><li>One effect reducing the target's hit point maximum</li></ul></div>",
